":null,"comments":[{"author":"Joe Oakhart","author_email":"joeoakhart+bot@navapbc.com","author_id":"594c-9dcf-5ad6-4e6d","body":"Validation resumed after terminal interruption: runner-envelope fix passes its focused regression test; full affected suite is green (62 passed), and make check passes Ruff, formatting, workflow lint, DCO identity, and mypy.","timestamp":1784760157348208001},{"author":"Joe Oakhart","author_email":"joeoakhart+bot@navapbc.com","author_id":"594c-9dcf-5ad6-4e6d","body":"Pushed Gerrit change 906 after rebase onto current origin/main. Local evidence: make check green; affected suite 62 passed; broad non-integration/non-external suite 6,980 passed, 28 skipped. Awaiting LLM-Review +1 and Verified +1.","timestamp":1784760864555385001},{"author":"Joe Oakhart","author_email":"joeoakhart+bot@navapbc.com","author_id":"594c-9dcf-5ad6-4e6d","body":"Gerrit 906 earned Verified +1 with all 20 CI jobs green. Zero unresolved comments; awaiting LLM-Review.","timestamp":1784762428766663001}],"created_at":1784759156378455001,"creation_channel":"cli","deps":[{"link_uuid":"3b72f89c-01f7-44ac-a0bd-5c62ef05fbe3","relation":"discovered_from","target_id":"7c27-10fc-4fe6-4b56"}],"description":"## Goal\nEnsure live focused prerequisite finder responses are normalized from the structured payload even when the runner adds standard metadata fields.\n\n## Current Behavior / Reproduction\nA live focused request returns valid `records` plus top-level `runner`, `model`, `trace_id`, and `_usage`. `normalize_coverage_records` validates the entire response against an extra-forbid payload model, catches the validation error, and converts every expected record to `indeterminate/output-invalid`. The live singleton evaluation reproduced recall 0.0 and validity 0.0; the same request passed when inspected directly.\n\n## Implementation\n- Add a RED contract test using a production-shaped response with records plus runner/model/trace/_usage metadata.\n- Normalize only the registered `records` payload while continuing to reject malformed, missing, duplicate, unknown, or cross-attributed records.\n\n## Verification\nRun the focused prerequisite unit suite and the live singleton prerequisite packing evaluation.\n\n## Acceptance Criteria\n- [ ] A valid production-shaped focused response with standard runner metadata yields its finding/consistent records rather than output-invalid.\n- [ ] Unknown fields inside the records payload remain rejected fail-closed.\n- [ ] Existing malformed-output and attribution tests remain green.","env_id":"ade0f2ef-51cc-45a2-bb97-c09846cd3df5","file_impact":[{"path":"src/rebar/llm/plan_review/prerequisites.py","reason":"Normalize the structured records payload while tolerating runner envelope metadata."},{"path":"tests/unit/test_plan_review_prerequisites.py","reason":"Add the production-shaped RED regression oracle."}],"keyring":[],"last_status_env_id":"ade0f2ef-51cc-45a2-bb97-c09846cd3df5","managed_refs":[["parent","jira-reb-1160"]],"parent_id":"jira-reb-1160","parent_status_uuid":"d8674103-142d-45aa-8745-2840109e4221","plan_review_phase":"execution","preconditions_summary":{"status":"pre-manifest"},"priority":2,"reverts":[],"status":"in_progress","tags":["regression","plan-review"],"ticket_id":"9417-a700-297d-4701","ticket_type":"bug","title":"Accept runner metadata on focused prerequisite output","verify_commands":[]},"source_event_uuids":["170df427-7bb8-43de-b626-4d22744a93a1","3b72f89c-01f7-44ac-a0bd-5c62ef05fbe3","8617bab5-27be-47b1-9fc1-0dda10f670f3","1a9043c6-553d-4a18-8f94-03bcfd33dcf3","00845a6b-9994-427a-b484-b4e2bd225084","d8674103-142d-45aa-8745-2840109e4221","d68b8f57-4239-4ebe-860d-d7693dc0582a","576a853f-0f06-4d92-b9fb-a89e2158be60","1a2686f2-6e77-48e2-b088-21eb5fb524f1","6c3560fd-d95b-4b04-8bc2-1122a9a6b2fb","9b5f0926-927f-4b46-a3ac-5ad64bdf0697"]},"env_id":"ade0f2ef-51cc-45a2-bb97-c09846cd3df5","event_type":"SNAPSHOT","timestamp":1784762428766663002,"uuid":"1f51ec4a-3cae-4ae2-9bd2-71c439a20688"}